        {
            "title": "川普警告將加強對伊朗打擊後能源股飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QQV9NxzKlZ85NSAvCyEX0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB3J0Y1_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週四能源公司股價攀升,油氣價格飆漲,此前美國總統唐納德·川普表示美國將繼續對伊朗進行軍事打擊,引發市場對全球石油供應長期中斷的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間07:25的盤前交易中,雪佛龍(Chevron)和埃克森美孚(Exxon Mobil)股價分別上漲3%和3.4%,康菲石油(ConocoPhillips)也攀升3.1%。更廣泛的XLE ETF (NYSE:XLE)上漲2.9%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c5ce702c-eb11-3661-8ac1-69224d1b8aaf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">布蘭特原油期貨上漲近8%至109.12美元/桶,而美國西德克薩斯中質原油期貨上漲8.7%至108.84美元。兩個基準在前一交易日回落後,開盤時曾小幅走低。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在電視講話中,川普表示美軍將在未來幾週加強對伊朗的攻勢,並將其定位為阻止德黑蘭獲得核武器。\"我們將在未來兩到三週內極其猛烈地打擊他們。我們將把他們帶回他們應該待的石器時代,\"他說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普補充說\"討論正在進行中\",但沒有表明停火是否即將到來。這番言論強化了早前曾短暫安撫市場的信號。週三,川普曾告訴記者,即使沒有正式協議,美國也可能在\"兩到三週內\"從伊朗撤軍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在發表演講前,川普在社交媒體上發文稱伊朗\"新政權總統\"已請求停火,似乎為談判打開了大門。伊朗外交部否認了這一說法,官方媒體報導稱德黑蘭並未尋求停戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普沒有提供任何可能導致荷莫茲海峽重新開放的措施細節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著衝突加劇,航運威脅不斷增加。卡達國防部表示,週三一艘租賃給卡達能源公司(QatarEnergy)的油輪在卡達水域遭到伊朗巡航導彈襲擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一些市場參與者表示,他們已停止交易以杜拜中東基準定價的貨物,該基準通常用於為全球近五分之一的原油供應定價,原因是無法使用荷莫茲海峽內的港口。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%B0%8D%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E5%BE%8C%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E8%82%A1%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-122253157.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 20:37:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美銀:英國央行將先升息後降息,能源衝擊持續",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wwIi1eNosr5D3CRzCCFOrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_2_M_1440048332.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國銀行(Bank of America)目前預期,英國央行將在轉向降息之前先升息兩次,因高能源價格增加了第二輪通膨效應蔓延至英國整體經濟的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀利率策略師Agne Stengeryte在給客戶的報告中表示,該行經濟學家目前預測2026年6月和7月將各升息25點子,隨後在2027年4月、7月和11月各降息25點子,這將使英國基準利率降至3.50%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司指出,風險偏向終端利率為3.25%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cccf32d4-3b91-3233-90d1-79dedbd29376-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項修正預測反映了美銀的預期,即由於中東衝突,能源價格將在2026年之前持續處於高位,促使貨幣政策委員會採取預防措施,以防通膨更加根深蒂固。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過,該公司也指出,若情況改善,可能出現升息一次即止的情境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在市場動態方面,美銀認為英國利率曲線的短端可能會比目前遠期定價所暗示的更急劇趨平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Stengeryte寫道:\"當英國央行首次升息時,市場最初可能會過度反應而走跌,但若英國央行認識到經濟增長前景較弱而轉向更鴿派立場時,曲線可能會進一步走陡。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀偏好的交易策略是支付2026年7月利率,同時收取2027年4月貨幣政策委員會日期的SONIA利率,這一部位旨在捕捉預期的近期趨平走勢,以及2027年最終轉向寬鬆政策的機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%87%E5%85%88%E5%8D%87%E6%81%AF%E5%BE%8C%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-121128705.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 20:37:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
